#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Transactions"
msgstr "Pretraga transakcija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:13
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Search Transactions</guilabel> dialog searches your data "
#| "based on criteria that you specify. You can access the dialog by going to "
#| "the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu and selecting <guimenuitem>Find "
#| "transaction...</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"You can use the <guilabel>Search transactions</guilabel> dialog to search "
"your data for transactions based on criteria that you specify. You can "
"access the dialog by selecting the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find transaction...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, or "
"typing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Dijalog za <guilabel>Pretraga transakcija</guilabel> pretražuje vaše podakte "
"na osnovu kriterija koji ste specificirali. Možete pristupiti dijalogu "
"odlaskom u <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> meni i odabirom <guimenuitem>Pronađi "
"transakciju...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:21
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When the <guibutton>Find</guibutton> button is pressed, the search is "
#| "initiated and all criteria that have been entered on any tab will be "
#| "taken into account."
msgid ""
"There are two main tabs in this dialog. The <guilabel>Criteria</guilabel> "
"tab displays a number of subtabs for specifying the search criteria. When "
"the <guibutton>Find</guibutton> button is pressed, the search is initiated "
"and all criteria that have been entered on any of the Criteria subtabs will "
"be taken into account."
msgstr ""
"Kada je pritisnuto dugme <guibutton>Pronađi</guibutton>, pretraga je "
"započeta i svi kriteriji uneseni u bilo kojoj kartici će biti uzeti u obzir."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:29
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The results will be displayed under the <quote>Result</quote> tab after "
#| "the search has completed. Below the list of results, &kappname; shows the "
#| "number of transactions that met the search criteria. Double-clicking on "
#| "an individual transaction in the result list will bring up the "
#| "appropriate ledger and display the transaction."
msgid ""
"After the search has completed, the results will be displayed under the "
"<guilabel>Result</guilabel> tab. Below the list of results, &kmymoney; shows "
"the number of transactions that met the search criteria. Double-clicking an "
"individual transaction in the result list will bring up the appropriate "
"ledger with that transaction selected."
msgstr ""
"Rezultati će biti prikazani pod karticom <quote>Rezultat</quote> nakon "
"završetka pretrage. Ispod liste rezultata, &kappname; prikazuje transakcije "
"koje zadovaljavaju kriterij pretrage. Duplim klikom na određenu transakciju "
"rezultat će prikazati odgovarajuću knjigu salda i prikazati transakciju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:37
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button resets all of the fields on all "
#| "of the criteria sub-tabs back to the defaults. This allows you to specify "
#| "new search criteria."
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button resets all of the fields on all of "
"the criteria subtabs back to the defaults. This allows you to specify new "
"search criteria."
msgstr ""
"Dugme <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> ponovno postavlja sva polja na svim pod-"
"karticama kriterija nazad na originalne vrijednosti. Ovo vam dozvoljava da "
"specificirate novi kriterij pretrage."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button closes the <guilabel>Search "
"Transactions</guilabel> dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Dugme  <guibutton>Zatvori</guibutton> zatvara dijalogni okvir "
"<guilabel>Pretraži transakcije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Criteria"
msgstr "Kriterij pretrage"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:49
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are several sub-tabs under the main <quote>Criteria</quote> tab, "
#| "each of which allows you to specify different types of search criteria. "
#| "Below the area for specifying the criteria, &kappname; lists each of the "
#| "different types of criteria that are currently specified for the search."
msgid ""
"There are several subtabs under the main Criteria tab, each of which allows "
"you to specify a different type of search criteria. Below the area for "
"specifying the criteria, &kmymoney; lists each of the different types of "
"criteria that are currently specified for the search."
msgstr ""
"U glavnoj kartici <quote>Kriterij</quote> se nalazi nekoliko pod-kartica, "
"svaka vam dozvoljava da specificirate različite vrste kriterija pretrage. "
"Ispod područja za specifikaciju kriterija, &kappname; izlistava svaku od "
"vrsta pretrage koji su trenutno određeni za pretragu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-search.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Tekst"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-search.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>search transactions, criteria tab, text subtab</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-search.docbook:64
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Search transactions Dialog, Text tab"
msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, text subtab</phrase>"
msgstr "Dijalog za pretragu transakcija, Tekstualna kartica"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:69
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This tab allows you to specify text to search for. There are also two "
#| "check boxes that control how the text is used in the search."
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to specify text to search for. There are also a dropdown "
"field and two check boxes that control how the text is used in the search."
msgstr ""
"Ova kartica vam dozvoljava da odredite tekst koji želite tražiti. Također, "
"tu su dva komandna okvira koja kontrolišu kako se tekst koristi u pretrazi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:74
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "By default, this will match on simple substrings. For example:"
msgid "By default, the search will match on simple substrings. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Kako je unaprijed definisano, ova opcija će dati poklapanje na jednostavnim "
"podnizovima znakova. Naprimjer:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<quote>Best</quote> will find <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"
msgstr "<quote>Najbolji</quote> će pronaći <quote>Najbolji kolači doo</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "<quote>est</quote> will also find <quote>Best Cakes, Inc.</quote>"
msgstr ""
"<quote>ajbolji</quote> će također pronaći <quote>Najbolji kolači doo</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the dropdown field next to the text field, select <guilabel>Contains</"
"guilabel> if you want to find transactions that contain the text, or select "
"<guilabel>Does not contain</guilabel> if you want to find transactions that "
"do not contain the specified text."
msgstr ""
"U opadajućem polju koje se nalazi pored polja za tekst, odaberite "
"<guilabel>Sadrži</guilabel> ako želite pronaći transakcije koje sadrže taj "
"tekst, ili odaberite <guilabel>Ne sadrži</guilabel> ako želite naći "
"transakcije koje ne sadrže uneseni tekst."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Case Sensitive</guilabel> box, the search will be "
"case sensitive. For example, <quote>best</quote> would not find <quote>Best "
"Cakes, Inc.</quote> if this option is set."
msgstr ""
"Ako zakačite <guilabel>Osjetljiv na velika i mala slova</guilabel> okvir, "
"pretraga će biti osjeljiva na velika i mala slova. Naprimjer, "
"<quote>najbolji</quote> ne bi pronašlo <quote>Najbolji kolači doo</quote> "
"ako je ova opcija podešena."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:104
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you check the <guilabel>Treat Text as regular expression</guilabel> "
#| "box, the text will be treated as a regular expression. For details on how "
#| "to craft a regular expression, visit the &Qt; documentation about the "
#| "<ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/doc/qt-4.8/qregexp.html#1\">QRegExp "
#| "class</ulink>."
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Treat Text as regular expression</guilabel> box, "
"the text will be treated as a regular expression. For details on how to "
"craft a regular expression, visit the &Qt; documentation about the <ulink "
"url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html\">QRegularExpression "
"class</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ako zakačite <guilabel>Tretiraj tekst kao obični izraz</guilabel> okvir, "
"tekst će biti tretiran kao obični izraz. Za detalje kako napraviti obični "
"izraze, posjetite  &Qt; dokumentaciju o <ulink url=\"http://qt-project.org/"
"doc/qt-4.8/qregexp.html#1\">QRegExp class</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
