msgid "<phrase>search transactions, criteria tab, payee subtab</phrase>"
msgstr "Dijalog za pretragu transakcija, Kartica primatelja uplata"

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tab allows you to specify which payees should be searched."
msgstr ""
"Ova kartica vam omogućava da specificirate koji primatelji uplate bi trebali "
"biti traženi."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:275
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Payees that are marked for search are indicated with a box. If you click "
#| "the <guibutton>All</guibutton> button, all payees are marked for "
#| "searching. If you click the <guibutton>None</guibutton> button, no payees "
#| "will be marked for searching. Individual payees can be marked or unmarked "
#| "by clicking on the box next to the payee name."
msgid ""
"Payees that are marked for search are indicated with a box. If you click "
"<guibutton>Select all</guibutton>, all payees are marked for searching. If "
"you click <guibutton>Select none</guibutton>, no payees will be marked for "
"searching. Individual payees can be marked or unmarked by clicking the box "
"next to the payee name."
msgstr ""
"Primatelji uplata koji su označeni za pretragu su naznačeni okvirom. Ako "
"kliknete na dugme <guibutton>Svi</guibutton>, svi primatelji uplata su "
"označeni za pretragu. Ako kliknete na dugme <guibutton>Nijedan</guibutton> , "
"nijedan primatelj uplate neće biti označen za pretragu. Pojedinačni "
"primatelji uplata mogu biti označeni ili odznačeni klikom na okvir pored "
"imena primatelja uplate."

#. Tag: para
#: details-search.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check the <guilabel>Select transactions without payees</guilabel> "
"box, only transactions with no payee will be selected."
msgstr ""
"Ako zakačite okvir <guilabel>Odaberi transakcije bez primatelja uplata</"
"guilabel>, samo transakcije bez primatelja uplate će biti odabrane."

